{"id":17865,"date":"2022-12-31T04:14:15","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:14:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:14:15","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:14:15","slug":"ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-2\/","title":{"rendered":"K\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u00f3a c\u1ee7a Lexus t\u1ea1i VMS 2022"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<ul class=\"social_left\">\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"myvne_save_for_later\" data-token=\"45ba1004a4f96ced9e1aa6c0defe637e\" data-article-id=\"4530731\" title=\"L\u01b0u b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft\">\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li_comment\"><span class=\"number_cmt txt_num_comment num_cmt_detail\" data-type=\"comment\" data-objecttype=\"7\" data-objectid=\"4530731\"><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span class=\"tip\">Quay l\u1ea1i Xe h\u01a1i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x156.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x533.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x400.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1536x800.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x313.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1920w\"><br \/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_753_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449848_753_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_753_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x56.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_753_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x192.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_753_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x144.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_753_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x113.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_753_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y Lexus t\u1ea1i Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m \u00d4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VMS) 2022 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi cho h\u00e3ng xe sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.  L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00e3ng n\u00e0y tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eabu xe \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u2013 Lexus LF-Z, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai m\u1eabu xe th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng NX 350h v\u00e0 ES 300h. <\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i xu h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u00f3a, gian h\u00e0ng Lexus t\u1ea1i VMS c\u00f3 khu tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y Phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng sang tr\u1ecdng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i LX 600 v\u00e0 LM 350.  Kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Immersive Lounge, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u m\u00e2y, tre, tr\u00fac\u2026 quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_283_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449848_283_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_283_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x127.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_283_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x432.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_283_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x324.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_283_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1536x648.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_283_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x253.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449848_283_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1920w\"><br \/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_863_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449849_863_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_863_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x43.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_863_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x147.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_863_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x110.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_863_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x86.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_863_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u00f3a, Lexus th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng qua kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u1ea1i VMS 2022. Tr\u00ean t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o, c\u00e1c d\u1ea3i thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u00e0u xanh d\u01b0\u01a1ng mang c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt.  Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a khu tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y mang xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng, n\u01a1i t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p>T\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e3ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00e0nh cho LF-Z, m\u1eabu xe mang t\u00ednh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Lexus trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t l\u00e1i, ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.  C\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh logo Lexus v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee5c khu\u1ef7u v\u00e0o ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200btr\u00fac t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng th\u00e2n xe tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.  Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ngo\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a LF-Z s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra xu h\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe Lexus trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p>Tazuna, thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt ch\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng d\u00e2y c\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n ng\u1ef1a.  \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng gi\u00fap c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ea1o ra khoang l\u00e1i tr\u00ean LF-Z.  Tri\u1ebft l\u00fd n\u00e0y l\u1ea5y con ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m trung t\u00e2m, nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n.  T\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft trong cabin \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp, ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i. <\/p>\n<p>\u201cD\u1ea5u \u1ea5n tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e1i Lexus\u201d \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t l\u1ef1c k\u00e9o d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ed1n b\u00e1nh Direct 4, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng l\u00e1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed Steer by Wire v\u00e0 tr\u00ed tu\u1ec7 nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o AI ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn.  LF-Z \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 ri\u00eang tr\u00ean t\u1eebng tr\u1ee5c, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n linh ho\u1ea1t gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u sau, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c hay v\u00e0o cua.  H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng l\u00e1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed Steer by Wire lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng qua tr\u1ee5c l\u00e1i, cung c\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp h\u01a1n gi\u1eefa h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00e1i v\u00e0 l\u1ef1c l\u00e1i. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_455_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449849_455_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_455_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x184.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_455_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x628.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_455_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x471.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_455_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1536x942.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_455_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x368.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_455_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh, Lexus ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a LF-Z d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200bs\u1ebd c\u00f3 ph\u1ea1m vi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 600 km sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n s\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ea7y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c t\u1eeb 0-100 km .  \/h trong 3 gi\u00e2y. <\/p>\n<p>Giri Venkatesh, Ph\u00f3 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lexus Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cTr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u, Lexus \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i xe th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, xe hybrid t\u1ef1 s\u1ea1c, xe hybrid c\u1eafm \u0111i\u1ec7n, xe ch\u1ea1y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 pin nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u.  Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng cho bi\u1ebft.  \u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f9y v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed7i qu\u1ed1c gia, Lexus s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t. T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Lexus d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hybrid. Th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u th\u00eam xe \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec7n\u201d. <\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i LF-Z, gian tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y Lexus t\u1ea1i VMS 2022 c\u00f2n gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i xe hybrid th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng NX 350h v\u00e0 ES 300h.  Trong \u0111\u00f3, NX 350h l\u00e0 m\u1eabu crossover h\u1ea1ng sang l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ra m\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4, l\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u xu h\u01b0\u1edbng cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 d\u1ea3i s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Lexus tr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u.  N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u01b0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed 12,3 inch, 17 loa Mark Levinson cao c\u1ea5p, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n LSS th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 th\u1ee9 3, camera 360 \u0111\u1ed9\u2026<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_300_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449849_300_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_300_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x117.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_300_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x399.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_300_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x300.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_300_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1536x599.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_300_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x234.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_300_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p>NX 350h s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng h\u00fat kh\u00ed t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, dung t\u00edch 2.5, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 188 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c, s\u1ee9c k\u00e9o 240 Nm.  M\u00f4-t\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn \u1edf tr\u1ee5c sau cho c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 240 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c k\u00e9o 360 Nm.  H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 CVT v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00e1nh.  Xe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 3,3 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng. <\/p>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh NX 350h t\u1ea1i tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m l\u00e0 m\u1eabu sedan h\u1ea1ng sang ES 300h, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Lexus t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.  Xe c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t h\u00ecnh con su\u1ed1t c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn.  C\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng micro LED, \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb ban ng\u00e0y \u0103n kh\u1edbp v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3.  N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00e1ch \u00e2m Hybrid Acoustic, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 l\u1edbp v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u gi\u00fap h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n, mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng gian y\u00ean t\u0129nh v\u00e0 ri\u00eang t\u01b0 cho h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch. <\/p>\n<p>ES 300h s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 hybrid 2,5 l\u00edt, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 176 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c.  M\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e3ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u1edf m\u1ee9c 4,6 l\u00edt\/100 km.  Xe c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 3,1 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_444_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449849_444_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_444_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x43.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_444_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x147.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_444_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x110.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_444_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x86.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_444_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u00f3a, Lexus \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem v\u00e0o h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe sang h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u.  Trong kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u n\u00e2u t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u1ea5m c\u00fang v\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng, tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y b\u1ed9 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng tinh x\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Lexus. <\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3ng Nh\u1eadt tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu SUV c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn LX 600 VIP v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ti\u1ec7n nghi cao c\u1ea5p nh\u01b0: 7 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 massage, l\u01b0ng ng\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a g\u00f3c 48 \u0111\u1ed9, g\u00e1c ch\u00e2n Ottoman, 11 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed.  6 inch\u2026 cho h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau. <\/p>\n<p>M\u1eabu MPV h\u1ea1ng sang tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u1ea1i tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m l\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 4 ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a LM 350. Xe s\u1edf h\u1eefu cabin \u201ch\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t\u201d v\u1edbi d\u00e0n \u00e2m thanh Mark Levinson 19 loa cao c\u1ea5p, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed 26 inch, massage. ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, h\u1ed9p l\u1ea1nh\u2026 cho h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau. <\/p>\n<p>\u201cLM \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eaft l\u1ecdc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec tinh t\u00fay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe sang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ebf t\u00e1c ri\u00eang cho nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ed1i \u0111a tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh\u201d, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n h\u00e3ng cho bi\u1ebft.  \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Lexus trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 phong c\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng di \u0111\u1ed9ng sang tr\u1ecdng m\u1edbi.\u201d <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_849_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449849_849_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_849_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x232.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_849_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x791.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_849_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x593.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_849_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1536x1186.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_849_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x463.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_849_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1920w\"><br \/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_211_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449849_211_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_211_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x43.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_211_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x147.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_211_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x110.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_211_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x86.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449849_211_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7t ngay sau ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t ch\u1ea5m ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1ea5t th\u01a1 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Lexus \u2013 kh\u00f4ng gian tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Immersive Lounge.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng gian, h\u00e3ng xe sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng KTS L\u00ea H\u00f9ng Tr\u1ecdng, mang \u0111\u1ebfn VMS 2022 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1ee9c m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1c quan, v\u1edbi ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i, h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc.  thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean h\u00e0i h\u00f2a. <\/p>\n<p>Immersive Lounge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb con ng\u01b0\u1eddi, dung h\u00f2a c\u00e1c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.  T\u00ednh ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e3ng xe sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u \u0111\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ea5t, g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0 m\u00e2y, tre, n\u1ee9a\u2026 <\/p>\n<p>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 d\u00f2ng ch\u1ea3y c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, KTS L\u00ea H\u00f9ng Tr\u1ecdng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cH\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh m\u00e1i v\u00f2m m\u00e2y t\u1ea1i khu tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0ng cho d\u00f2ng ch\u1ea3y \u2013 m\u1ed9t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i c\u00e1c gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u0103n h\u00f3a, nh\u00e2n v\u0103n, qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\u201d. s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e2y, tre, tr\u00fac v\u00e0 c\u00e1c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng kh\u00e1c g\u1eafn k\u1ebft s\u00e2u s\u1eafc v\u1edbi v\u0103n h\u00f3a v\u00e0 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam.  Lexus v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eb1ng ki\u1ebfn \u200b\u200btr\u00fac b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng,\u201d \u00f4ng n\u00f3i.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_956_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672449850_956_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_956_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_956_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x691.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_956_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x518.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_956_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1536x1036.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_956_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x405.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_956_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p>Khu v\u1ef1c Immersive Lounge mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1ee9c c\u00e1c gi\u00e1c quan c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u01a1ng hoa t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u00e1t c\u1ee7a thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.  Kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb loa \u00e2m thanh v\u00f2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Mark Levinson. <\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n h\u01a1n, Lexus \u0111\u01b0a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u g\u1ea7n g\u0169i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5u v\u00e0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp mang \u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i.  \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa c\u00e0 ph\u00ea mu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 b\u00e1nh Yokan.  V\u1ecb \u0111\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e0 ph\u00ea h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi v\u1ecb m\u1eb7n c\u1ee7a mu\u1ed1i, b\u00ean tr\u00ean l\u00e0 l\u1edbp b\u1ecdt s\u1eefa b\u1ed3ng b\u1ec1nh, t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00eam v\u1ecb ng\u1ecdt th\u01a1m c\u1ee7a l\u1edbp cacao mang logo Lexus.  C\u00f9ng l\u1edbp h\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u1ecb ng\u1ecdt c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng l\u1edbp b\u00e1nh Yokan \u0111\u1eadu \u0111\u1ecf \u1ea9n ch\u1ee9a n\u00e9t tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.  Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft th\u00fac b\u1edfi k\u1eb9o kh\u00f4 Rakugan.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ed9 th\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m Lexus th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u xanh lai.  B\u00e1nh Foret Blueu t\u1eeb tr\u00e0 xanh k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi d\u00e2u \u0111en m\u1ec1m ng\u1ecdt, th\u00eam ch\u00fat \u0111\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u00e1t socola mang logo Lexus.  Mocktail xanh \u0111\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u00e1t v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u01a1ng soda b\u1ea1c h\u00e0, h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi v\u1ea3i thi\u1ec1u chua chua mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb trung \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Lexus mang \u0111\u1ebfn VMS n\u0103m nay.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_202_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" title=\"1672449850_202_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_202_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_202_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_202_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_202_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_202_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 tinh t\u1ebf, t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a Lexus c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp.  L\u00e0 h\u00e3ng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean g\u00e1c c\u1eeda \u2013 ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng m\u1edf c\u1eeda, c\u00fai ch\u00e0o t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00f4ng gian Immersive Lounge.  T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u1eef kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft nhanh nhu c\u1ea7u.  \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng minh ch\u1ee9ng cho cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Lexus trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1eb7t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m trung t\u00e2m, th\u1ea5m nhu\u1ea7n tinh th\u1ea7n Omotenashi \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Tr\u1ea7n H\u00f9ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn Showroom Lexus BST \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u2013 Carbon Neutral Fashion Collection.  \u0110\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u201ch\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng th\u00f4ng qua ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi trang\u201d, quy tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y m\u00f3c, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t.  \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Tr\u1ea7n H\u00f9ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u Scoby (Gi\u1ea5m). <\/p>\n<p>Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m VMS 2022 \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng 10 n\u0103m, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Lexus ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2012. Trong 10 n\u0103m qua, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Lexus cho bi\u1ebft, h\u00e3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a h\u01a1n 10.000 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m VMS 2022. th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.  tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc sang ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp theo, Lexus ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u0111am m\u00ea t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c, ti\u00ean phong m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111i\u1ec7n kh\u00ed h\u00f3a v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u.  c\u01a1 quan chia s\u1ebb. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_969_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg\" title=\"1672449850_969_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_969_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-300x149.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_969_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1024x508.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_969_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-768x381.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_969_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-1536x762.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_969_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022-600x298.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672449850_969_ky-nguyen-dien-khi-hoa-cua-lexus-tai-vms-2022.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">N\u1ed9i dung: Quang Anh \u2013 <span style=\"text-align:left;\">T\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh: <\/span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">Lexus Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf: Th\u00e1i H\u01b0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Quay l\u1ea1i Xe h\u01a1i Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y Lexus t\u1ea1i Tri\u1ec3n l\u00e3m \u00d4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VMS) 2022 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi cho h\u00e3ng xe sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00e3ng n\u00e0y tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y t\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eabu xe \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thu\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":15611,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"hr